en_121188_0	The Avant Garde Company says that it refutes the report that Additional Solicitor General Wasantha Navaratne Bandara submitted to the Attorney General.
en_121188_1	Former senior merchant vessel manager retired Lieutenant Colonel Nilantha Jayaweera said so while participating at the media briefing held in Colombo yesterday.
en_121188_2	Additional Solicitor General Wasantha Navaratne Bandara submitted a report to the Attorney General with regard to the vessel containing a floating armoury called ‘Mahanuwara’ that Avant Garde had rented out.
en_121188_3	That was on the basis of an investigation the CID had carried out.
